Celeste O'Connor (a mụrụ na Disemba 2, 1998) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri America amụrụ na Kenya
A maara ha maka igwu egwu Paloma Davis na ihe nkiri mbụ Amazon, Selah and the Spades
A mụrụ Celeste O'Connor na Disemba 2, n'afọ 1998, na Nairobi, Kenya
Nne na nna ha zụlitere O'Connor na nwanne ha nwoke nke nta na Baltimore, Maryland. Ha gara Notre Dame Preparatory School ma mụọ violin na ịbụ abụ na Peabody Preparatory

O'Connor na-aga Mahadum Johns Hopkins ma na-amụ banyere ahụike ọha na eze na ọgwụ. Ha agakwaala ọmụmụ ihe n'ihe ọmụmụ Islam. O'Connor nwere mmasị na ihe ndị na-ekpebi mmekọrịta mmadụ na ibe ya nke ahụike gụnyere nchekwa nri, enweghị ụlọ, na agụmakwụkwọ.

O'Connor mere ihe nkiri nke Gugu Mbatha-Raw na ihe nkiri Netflix nke afọ 2018, Irreplaceable You Ha pụtara na ihe nkiri afọ 2019, Wetlands N'afọ 2019, O'Connor mere Paloma Davis na ihe nkiri, Selah and the Spades Onye nta akụkọ Anagha Komaragiri nke The Daily Californian toro O'Connor "n'ụzọ dị nro" na "ọnụnọ dị oké ọnụ ahịa" ruo mgbe "ọgwụgwụ siri ike". A họpụtara O'Connor na ọnwa July afọ 2019 maka ihe nkiri afọ 2021, Ghostbusters: Afterlife O'Connor abụghị nke abụọ.
O'Connor bụ onye na-akwado imeziwanye ọdịiche na nnọchi anya na ụlọ ọrụ ntụrụndụ.
